queries.sql: SELECT `b`.`warehouseName`, SUM(CASE WHEN a.status IN (0, 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS review, SUM(CASE WHEN a.status = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS close, COUNT(a.request_id) AS total FROM `request` `a` LEFT JOIN `tblwarehouse` `b` ON `b`.`warehouseID` = `a`.`from` GROUP BY `a`.`from`, `b`.`warehouseName` ORDER BY `a`.`from` ASC
